y &= -4 \left(-\frac{7}{4}\right) \left(-\frac{5}{4}\right) = 35,\\
z &= -4(-1) = 4.
\end{align*}

Therefore, the rectangular coordinates of the point with spherical coordinates $(\rho, \theta, -\phi)$ are $\boxed{(35, 35, 4)}$. I hope it is correct.

